{"tid":681774,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港天星小輪疑失控　二度衝撞尖沙嘴碼頭","createTime":"2018-05-28T10:17:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-28T19:36:55.000Z","uid":26332,"like":97,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"744386cf4aa782285d37dd35c694bc5969f02066","tid":681774,"uid":26332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T10:17:45.000Z","msg":"香港天星小輪疑失控　二度衝撞尖沙嘴碼頭<br />\n1141<br />\n建立時間：2018/05/28 17:46<br />\n<br />\n香港《蘋果日報》接獲讀者報料，今天(28日)下午，一艘往返港島與九龍間的「天星小輪」，在尖沙嘴碼頭失控撞向鄰近的海運大廈橋邊，該處有小吃攤與露天茶座。雖然小輪再撞上前曾鳴笛警告，提醒岸上的行人，但最後仍撞上岸邊的防撞欄，柵欄被撞到鬆脫下墮。<br />\n<br />\n下午5時許，一艘由港島中環開往尖沙嘴的天星小輪疑因失控，撞向鄰近海運大廈的橋邊，防撞欄嚴重損毀，鬆脫下墮。現場消息指出，小輪接近橋邊時一度鳴號，船上水手立即跑至船頭，協助坐在船頭附近的乘客向後移動，之後小輪的船邊撞上橋邊防撞欄，沒多久小輪再撞向橋邊。在附近露天茶座用餐的遊客見狀爭相走避，警方及消防人員正趕往現場，了解事件。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180528/1362678/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180528%2F1362678%2F&d=LJrlrQnCPRTkRTA%2FSLTgpQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=68783f00\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180528%2F1362678%2F&h=35e5a395\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180528/1362678/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180528/640_15490e9323e5f998e23358707e182190.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180528%2F640_15490e9323e5f998e23358707e182190.jpg&h=970d1dc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n天星啲船好硬正，撞完無爛，防撞欄反而斷左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b9cb6ff2cc42c7e3633da64a3ed2257a781bb34","tid":681774,"uid":810,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T10:18:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/l0MYtC4cHoHV1NmTK/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2Fl0MYtC4cHoHV1NmTK%2Fgiphy.gif&h=47269ad9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eeb1c1ec83a53d574778f1e5951d457c12faa1e4","tid":681774,"uid":26332,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T10:20:31.000Z","msg":"天星小輪失動力撞尖沙咀碼頭木躉　30乘客海上漂流<br />\n05月28日(一) 17:36   <br />\n出事小輪(左)由另一艘船協助拖返碼頭。(郭垂垂攝)<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180528/photo/bkn-20180528173651495-0528_00822_001_01p.jpg?20180528180324\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180528%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180528173651495-0528_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20180528180324&h=6064e8e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n出事小輪(左)由另一艘船協助拖返碼頭。(郭垂垂攝)<br />\n<br />\n天星小輪發生撞木躉意外。下午5時許，一輛載有約30名乘客的天星小輪，由中環開往尖沙嘴，臨近泊岸時疑突然失去動力，直撼海運大廈對開岸邊的木躉，繼而反彈回海中漂流，未幾再撞向木躉。期間小輪曾響號，岸上人士一度爭相走避。據了解，天星小輪已派出另一艘船接近涉事小輪，擬將其拖返岸邊，警方及消防趕至現場了解。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180528/mobile/bkn-20180528173651495-0528_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180528%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180528173651495-0528_00822_001.html&d=LJrlrQnCPRTkRTA%2FSLTgpQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=1acf4b1a\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180528/mobile/bkn-20180528173651495-0528_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"9660225b70720fb382acab93c7b9f7841acf8e96","tid":681774,"uid":3028,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T10:21:54.000Z","msg":"船長飲大左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5703c88bc1b78941312fb54fde621e3f3de6901","tid":681774,"uid":26332,"like":68,"dislike":0,"score":68,"quote":{"pid":"9660225b70720fb382acab93c7b9f7841acf8e96","tid":681774,"uid":3028,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T10:21:54.000Z","msg":"船長飲大左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T10:22:52.000Z","msg":"似係機件故障多啲"},{"pid":"91ec49cfe7b7a067eb6e1ad9df7f6d7648a6b416","tid":